[Bridge : Tablo]
Gentle rain on the rooftop
Let'em hide all my tear drops
When I cry and I pray god
Please make the pain stop
Gentle rain on the rooftop
Let'em hide all my tear drops
When I cry
And I pray god
Please make the pain stop
But the pain is all I got

